snippet.title: Slither.io™ Arcade
snippet.description: slither.io, a top-10 app on the App Store and the Google Play store, is finally coming to the arcade! The hit game is now available as a multiplayer arcade game with a giant 55″ display and 3 player positions in a compact cabinet.
